202
00:12:04,870 --> 00:12:06,180
He's only 30 years old.

203
00:12:06,990 --> 00:12:08,230
He's not much older than us.

204
00:12:09,350 --> 00:12:10,370
He built this academy from scratch

205
00:12:11,020 --> 00:12:12,060
and just started making a name for himself.

206
00:12:13,230 --> 00:12:14,430
It's been tough for him after striving for years.

207
00:12:15,580 --> 00:12:16,670
You ruined many years of his works

208
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:18,560
with your tantrum.

209
00:12:20,270 --> 00:12:21,840
Well, I think what I did was not even enough.

210
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:23,990
I should have burned this place to the ground.

211
00:12:28,750 --> 00:12:29,090
Let's go.

212
00:12:29,460 --> 00:12:30,000
Let's have one more match.

213
00:12:34,290 --> 00:12:34,840
Last week,

214
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:36,160
