216
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:40,720
So, the topic for today's meeting is

217
00:12:40,980 --> 00:12:43,500
how to prevent such an incident from happening again.

218
00:12:44,190 --> 00:12:45,650
We've been running these classes for four, five years now,

219
00:12:45,870 --> 00:12:47,320
