227
00:13:00,250 --> 00:13:01,830
Even if he sets this place on fire,

228
00:13:02,030 --> 00:13:03,870
I'll have to keep him within this ruins!

229
00:13:05,760 --> 00:13:07,040
If this person makes another mistake,

230
00:13:08,350 --> 00:13:09,170
leave it to me to handle.

231
00:13:10,020 --> 00:13:11,390
That would worsen the situation.

232
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:12,600
Mr. Yuan.

233
00:13:13,190 --> 00:13:15,000
